,Recommended,299720,32205395,Posted: 5 June,all,Dilapinated,"An ingenious, abstract & minimalist 3D tower defence game. Watch little geometric shapes crawl around labyrinthine objects as you build increasingly ridiculous trees of laser-death to make them explode into a rainbow of carnage.Gameplay is a mix of classic TD optimisation with plotting & extending your nodes to give the maximum amount of turrets (which each have a hemispherical firing arc) the maximum amount of roadspace to fire upon. ""just clump a bunch together around a slowing-turret"" definitely does not get you through levels alone here- Expect to fail a few times before you get the a) swing of it & b) unlocks to compete, even on easy mode. Thankfully the unlocks are frequent & generous, and can often change turrets in quite radical ways.Highly recommended, and an utter no-brainer for such a price. Mindwarping but hypnotic, minimalist but deep."
